	basic_am_demod.py
	Usage: python basic_am_demod.py <monowavfile.wav>
	Output: PNG of signal processing visualisation
1b. Calibration demo input for basic_am_demod.py:
	sine-200x5x6.wav
1c. Speech demo input for basic_am_demod.py:
	one-to-thirty-2044_04_22_11s_16k.wav

